    "Therefore, LMA systems must be capable of dynamically adjusting their scale, strategies, and structures throughout the development process.",
    "Current State.",
    "Most existing LMA systems [48,109] operate with static architectures characterized by fixed agent roles and predefined communication patterns.",
    "Recent research efforts [89,157] have introduced mechanisms for adaptive agent team selection and task-specific collaboration strategies.",
